The '''Allied Tion Historical Society''' was an organization based in [[Lola Curich]], [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]] that specialized in the study of the [[Tion Hegemony/Legends|Tion Hegemony]]. It was funded by [[Republic Sienar Systems/Legends|Republic Sienar Systems]], the [[House of Tion/Legends|House of Tion]], and the [[House of Cron]]. Just before the start of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], it hosted the "[[Cradle of the Galaxy]]" exhibit on [[Xim/Legends|Xim the Despot]]. Its director at that time was [[Alreeda Tion-Hyme]].

